make a recomendation?<br>
Well I am not going to wait around to see if someone says yes but since its patch time and I cannot sleep I was reading some of the threads on this board and as usual most are just the same people ranting about the same stuff, but anyway I digress from my purpose in posting, so here it is.<br>
Don't post your raids here or ask for who is going when.<br>
Why you ask? Well let me tell you why. Player X wants to go to the plane of hate and sees guild Y is planning the same day in an open forum as his guild X is planning in a private one, so what does player X do? He makes sure guild X is there before the time guild Y is planning so stupidly in front of everyone.<br>
Wouldn't it be nice if everyone helped everyone else and we all were just here to server the greater good of the community as a whole? LOL Hell no!!!<br>
Go on your raids. Plan them in secret and have a backup plan for the off chance that you are beaten to a plane or something is already killed and then have a backup plan for your backup plan. If at this point all is taken or dead move along and push the plans back a day or a week or 8 hours as the case may be.<br>
Getting all bent out of shape and starting fights will only ensure that the people you piss off will be there minutes before you with their tongues sticking out in your general direction.<br>
I don't intend this as a bashing post but more of a reality slap. Shit happens and it happens even more when we can hide behind our little safety screen where no one can see who we really are and to whom none of us will have to fess up when we are done knocking each other down and stealing each others toys.<br>
This game with guilds and all is more like a business and we are in the business of gathering loot for our members and in a very competitive business environment the only time one should allow the secrets to leak to the enemy is when its a ruse to head them in the wrong direction as you gather the loots for your people.<br>
Yes it is late and I tend to be lengthy when it is, but please take what is here and use it and you will have less stress and anger and maybe you can turn some of that into pride that you were able to go there first and accomplish your goals.<br>
--------------------<br>
Giggy<br>
Order of the Phoenix<br>
60th Level KING of the halfling clerics everywhere<br>
May the little people conquer and control all the world!!! <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#242422><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub12.ezboard.com/ukeronos.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Keronos</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_lightning.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 79<br> <font color=#DDA0DD>(8/14/01 3:26:53 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://members.chello.nl/~b.rohrbock/images/ezbpic.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: .</span><hr size=1> Totally agree with mr. halfling cleric king<br>
